I'm DaiDR, a front-end developer.

I'm maintaining:

  • Paimon-WebExt - Track Genshin Impact in-game stats in your browser

I'm developing:

  • Truth Table Generator - One-click generation of truth tables based on logical expressions
  • DuotuneCook - Generating duotone style images in seconds

I'm contributing to:

  • FastMirror(FE) - Minecraft server core mirror website(totally free)
  • Modpack Hub(FE) - Filter eligible CurseForge modpacks by mods list
